      "applicationProcess": [
        {
          "process": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 1:",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " Visit the Official Portal "
                },
                {
                  "type": "link",
                  "link": "https://ecms.meity.gov.in/",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "text": "www.ecms.meity.gov.in"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": " and click on \"Register\"."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 2: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Select your Type of Entity (Company / LLP), enter Registered Applicant Name, Company PAN, CIN / LLPIN, and Date of Incorporation."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 2: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Enter Name and Designation of the authorised signatory, set a Password, enter Email ID → click Send OTP → enter OTP, enter Mobile Number → click Send OTP → enter OTP."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 3: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Upload Certificate of Incorporation, Letter of Authorisation (on company letterhead, signed by Director), and PAN Card of Company."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 4: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Click the \"Register\" button → you will receive a confirmation on your email and mobile."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 5: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Log in using your registered email and password → start filling out your actual application form."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 7: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "Select your Target Segment (A / B / C / D / E) based on your product category"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 8:",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " Choose Incentive Type (Turnover-linked / Capex-linked / Hybrid) → fill in investment, sales, employment, and localisation details"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 9:",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " Pay the non-refundable Application Fee online → submit the form → save your Unique Application ID"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 10: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "PMA acknowledges within 15 working days → respond to any queries within 15 days → PMA forwards recommendations to the Governing Council (GC)"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 11: ",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": "GC sends for approval — Secretary MeitY (up to ₹100 Cr) or Minister of Electronics & IT (above ₹100 Cr) → begin manufacturing after approval"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": "Step 12:",
                  "bold": true
                },
                {
                  "text": " Submit annual incentive claims through the portal every financial year → PMA verifies and disburses incentives on a first-come, first-served basis"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "children": [
                {
                  "text": ""
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "mode": "Online",
          "process_md": "**Step 1:** Visit the Official Portal [www.ecms.meity.gov.in](https://ecms.meity.gov.in/) and click on &quot;Register&quot;.\n**Step 2:** Select your Type of Entity (Company / LLP), enter Registered Applicant Name, Company PAN, CIN / LLPIN, and Date of Incorporation.\n**Step 2:** Enter Name and Designation of the authorised signatory, set a Password, enter Email ID → click Send OTP → enter OTP, enter Mobile Number → click Send OTP → enter OTP.\n**Step 3:** Upload Certificate of Incorporation, Letter of Authorisation (on company letterhead, signed by Director), and PAN Card of Company.\n**Step 4:** Click the &quot;Register&quot; button → you will receive a confirmation on your email and mobile.\n**Step 5:** Log in using your registered email and password → start filling out your actual application form.\n**Step 7:** Select your Target Segment (A / B / C / D / E) based on your product category\n**Step 8:** Choose Incentive Type (Turnover-linked / Capex-linked / Hybrid) → fill in investment, sales, employment, and localisation details\n**Step 9:** Pay the non-refundable Application Fee online → submit the form → save your Unique Application ID\n**Step 10:** PMA acknowledges within 15 working days → respond to any queries within 15 days → PMA forwards recommendations to the Governing Council (GC)\n**Step 11:** GC sends for approval — Secretary MeitY (up to ₹100 Cr) or Minister of Electronics &amp; IT (above ₹100 Cr) → begin manufacturing after approval\n**Step 12:** Submit annual incentive claims through the portal every financial year → PMA verifies and disburses incentives on a first-come, first-served basis\n<br>\n\n"
